Utilities for working with pristine-tar-enabled repositories

BEWARE! This tool was written by somebody unfamiliar with gbp(1), so
there are likely better alternatives using gbp.

pristine-tar-utils:
	library providing common code for the various tools

ptu:
	tool for generating, extracting or cleaning a pristine-tar

debuild-pristine-tar:
	debuild(1) wrapper for building a pristine-tar-enabled
	repository easily, taking care of extracting the tarball
	and cleaning up afterwards.
	It also generates a temporary version suffix for the build.
